  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/ce22535032460695401e6049a19d2ef0.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/ce22535032460695401e6049a19d2ef0.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/108a525aee5122676b423adfdb82b430.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/108a525aee5122676b423adfdb82b430.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/5cfa2c0ac1667a5e249430af7c608882.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/5cfa2c0ac1667a5e249430af7c608882.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/f8ed26c4cb76d0ea2184c058c576395e.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/f8ed26c4cb76d0ea2184c058c576395e.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/c9af2d8b9d65d20d2a94ddf358b6f9f3.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/c9af2d8b9d65d20d2a94ddf358b6f9f3.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/fb4267c382492b70f2a84c3e80c979a1.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/fb4267c382492b70f2a84c3e80c979a1.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/f480695093d40903d32c43aa6151ccba.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/f480695093d40903d32c43aa6151ccba.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/4642131d99c70902f116b0edfb25c0ec.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/4642131d99c70902f116b0edfb25c0ec.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/f4d009b50f1be64c5affa84725665626.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/f4d009b50f1be64c5affa84725665626.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/6bc84c0ca8850af6639310f6be0407bb.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/6bc84c0ca8850af6639310f6be0407bb.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Last Reunion is an AI-powered deduction game where a joyful reunion ends in tragedy.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You play as a police officer investigating a murder that occurred during a house party.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the crime scene from a first-person perspective, interact with objects, and uncover hidden clues.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interrogate NPCs powered by ChatGPT, each designed with a unique personality, backstory, and secrets.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your investigation influences the storyline, and each suspect leads to a different ending.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replay the game to discover new evidence and uncover the full truth behind Alan’s death.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Immersive first-person investigation gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- ChatGPT-integrated NPCs that respond based on unique personas</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Interactive crime scene exploration and evidence collection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Multi-ending structure shaped by player choices</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Story-driven gameplay set in a single location with dynamic interrogation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Tips for Playing The Last Reunion]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1️⃣ Pay close attention to each character’s reaction.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The more sensitive the response, the more likely your question is tied to the case.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2️⃣ Gather as much evidence as possible first.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      This will help you build a solid overall picture of the incident.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3️⃣ Every character will eventually tire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The more you interrogate, the more hidden truths will come out.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4️⃣ Think carefully before asking questions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The wrong approach may lead to strange or misleading answers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5️⃣ Evidence is more than just an item.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      You need to connect it with other clues when questioning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👉 Experience it yourself now in *The Last Reunion*!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/ce22535032460695401e6049a19d2ef0.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/ce22535032460695401e6049a19d2ef0.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/108a525aee5122676b423adfdb82b430.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/108a525aee5122676b423adfdb82b430.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/5cfa2c0ac1667a5e249430af7c608882.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/5cfa2c0ac1667a5e249430af7c608882.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/f8ed26c4cb76d0ea2184c058c576395e.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/f8ed26c4cb76d0ea2184c058c576395e.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras/c9af2d8b9d65d20d2a94ddf358b6f9f3.avif?t=1755849025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3600510/extras_big/c9af2d8b9d65d20d2a94ddf358b6f9f3.avif?t=1755849025 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p cl