oyful reunion ends in tragedy.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You play as a police officer investigating a murder that occurred during a house party.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the crime scene from a first-person perspective, interact with objects, and uncover hidden clues.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interrogate NPCs powered by ChatGPT, each designed with a unique personality, backstory, and secrets.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your investigation influences the storyline, and each suspect leads to a different ending.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replay the game to discover new evidence and uncover the full truth behind Alan’s death.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Immersive first-person investigation gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- ChatGPT-integrated NPCs that respond based on unique personas</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Interactive crime scene exploration and evidence collection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Multi-ending structure shaped by player choices</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- Story-driven gameplay set in a single location with dynamic interrogation</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Tips for Playing The Last Reunion]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1️⃣ Pay close attention to each character’s reaction.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The more sensitive the response, the more likely your question is tied to the case.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2️⃣ Gather as much evidence as possible first.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      This will help you build a solid overall picture of the incident.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3️⃣ Every character will eventually tire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The more you interrogate, the more hidden truths will come out.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4️⃣ Think carefully before asking questions.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      The wrong approach may lead to strange or misleading answers.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5️⃣ Evidence is more than just an item.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      You need to connect it with other clues when questioning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👉 Experience it yourself now in *The Last Reunion*!</p>",
